    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>An extremely durable paint having pigment in a water-soluble silicon-containing binder such as sodium silicate and silicon ester. Silicate paints have been used in murals and stereochrome paintings, in appearance similar to fresco.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000042701/Wehlte, Materials and Techniques of Painting (1982)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000047822/MFA Conservation and Art Material Encyclopedia Online: CAMEO (2005-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Pintura extremadamente durable cuyo vehículo consiste fundamentalmente en vidrio soluble, utilizada especialmente para pintar sobre mortero o sobre enlucido seco. Puede ser difícil de distinguir del verdadero fresco.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Een uitermate duurzame verf waarvan het oplosmiddel hoofdzakelijk bestaat uit waterglas; wordt vooral gebruikt voor het verven op mortel, en soms op droog pleister. Is nauwelijks te onderscheiden van echt fresco.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052381/Van Dale Engels-Nederlands (1989)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>一種極度持久耐用之油漆，其展色劑主要成分為水玻璃，特別用於灰漿壁面上的繪畫，有時候也應用於乾燥的石膏上，其成品有可能跟真正的濕壁畫完全一樣，兩者難以分辨。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
